\begin_layout Exercise*
יהי 
\begin_inset Formula $V$
\end_inset

 ממ
\begin_inset Quotes erd
\end_inset

פ סוף-מימדי ויהי 
\begin_inset Formula $T:V\to V$
\end_inset

.
 הוכיחו כי 
\begin_inset Formula $\text{Ker}T^{\ast}=\left(\text{Im}T\right)^{\perp}$
\end_inset

.
